text: KFUM Jönköping is an YMCA association in Jönköping in Sweden. It was established in 1855. By the late 1980s and early 1990s the volleyboll team experienced a successful period. At that time, club club played in Elitserien at both the men's and women's sides. == References == ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1855 establishments in Europe Category:Sport in Jönköping Category:Volleyball clubs in Sweden Category:19th-century establishments in Sweden
